Review: I’m so conflicted! Some aspects shined more than the original, especially with Janice shining much more as a character as well as a lot of the messaging of the film. I just think that the idea of modernizing a movie and making it for a “new generation”  by adding TikTok and some iPhones where the audience of the movie still LOVES the first movie and probably has seen it feels like a bit of overreach. But the performances are pretty great and make up for it! iPad babies are gonna loveeee this one
